(Watch the glass. Stay safe.)

864
00:24:43,800 --> 00:24:44,920
Watch the glass. Stay safe.

865
00:24:44,920 --> 00:24:47,700
(The Puppet once appeared here)

866
00:24:47,800 --> 00:24:48,520
You go.

867
00:24:48,520 --> 00:24:49,440
Me? Really?

868
00:24:49,440 --> 00:24:49,680
Of course.

869
00:24:49,680 --> 00:24:50,000
No way.

870
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:52,000
I'll actually die.

871
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:52,920
You won't.

872
00:24:52,920 --> 00:24:53,240
Fine.

873
00:24:53,240 --> 00:24:53,840
(Humans aren't that fragile)

874
00:24:53,840 --> 00:24:54,480
I'll do it.

875
00:24:54,480 --> 00:24:54,720
Go.

876
00:24:56,260 --> 00:24:57,140
(Using his hand to open it)

877
00:24:57,160 --> 00:24:57,880
Wait.

878
00:24:58,800 --> 00:25:00,120
I have a bad feeling that...

879
00:25:00,120 --> 00:25:00,960
He's probably inside.

880
00:25:01,180 --> 00:25:02,160
(Is the Puppet hiding here?)

881
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:02,720
No.

882
00:25:03,540 --> 00:25:04,120
(Gripping tight)

883
00:25:04,120 --> 00:25:04,720
This is scary.

884
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:05,920
We'll stay behind.

885
00:25:05,920 --> 00:25:06,940
(Let the suspects go first)

886
00:25:07,680 --> 00:25:08,760
My poor little heart.

887
00:25:08,760 --> 00:25:09,840
I still need to sleep tonight.

888
00:25:09,840 --> 00:25:10,680
And I sleep alone.

889
00:25:10,960 --> 00:25:12,760
So does everyone.

890
00:25:14,080 --> 00:25:15,400
Same for all of us.

891
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:16,460
(That excuse is too common)

892
00:25:17,740 --> 00:25:20,300
(Singing away the fear)

893
00:25:21,920 --> 00:25:23,200
How do we open this?

894
00:25:24,120 --> 00:25:25,680
There's no way to open it.

895
00:25:25,740 --> 00:25:27,340
(The glass door is shut tight)

896
00:25:29,900 --> 00:25:31,540
(Watch the glass. Stay safe.)

897
00:25:36,820 --> 00:25:39,580
(Watch the glass. Stay safe.)

898
00:25:41,320 --> 00:25:42,600
This seems removable.

899
00:25:46,260 --> 00:25:46,420
(There's something behind it)

900
00:25:46,820 --> 00:25:48,300
(Push the door)

901
00:25:48,320 --> 00:25:49,000
Push the door.

902
00:25:51,720 --> 00:25:52,800
Do we need to push harder?

903
00:25:53,360 --> 00:25:54,240
Should we push together?

904
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:56,480
Is this the Door of Truth?

905
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:58,040
Or we need to push the door?

906
00:25:58,140 --> 00:26:00,100
(Door of Truth? Or push the door?)

907
00:26:00,240 --> 00:26:01,440
Let's try it.

908
00:26:01,740 --> 00:26:03,620
(Push)

909
00:26:04,040 --> 00:26:05,120
Bro, you're brave.

910
00:26:07,220 --> 00:26:08,580
(It won't budge)

911
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:12,360
Can we peel more?

912
00:26:14,900 --> 00:26:15,180
(Push the door)

913
00:26:15,180 --> 00:26:16,480
(Door)

914
00:26:16,480 --> 00:26:16,880
Door.

915
00:26:18,440 --> 00:26:19,520
Keep peeling.

916
00:26:20,000 --> 00:26:21,480
Seems like a shackle.

917
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:23,240
(That door seems like a shackle)

918
00:26:23,240 --> 00:26:24,120
That door seems

919
00:26:24,120 --> 00:26:24,760
like a shackle.

920
00:26:24,760 --> 00:26:25,520
A shackle.

921
00:26:25,540 --> 00:26:26,660
(Wait)

922
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:28,520
Isn't this your song?

923
00:26:28,520 --> 00:26:30,000
(Fan mode again)
Isn't this your song, Ning?

924
00:26:30,520 --> 00:26:31,680
Trapping...

925
00:26:31,680 --> 00:26:33,700
("The Door" by Liu Yuning)

926
00:26:33,700 --> 00:26:35,780
(Live mode on)
♪Trapping me♪

927
00:26:35,800 --> 00:26:36,320
Keep going.

928
00:26:36,320 --> 00:26:38,880
♪I can't move♪

929
00:26:38,880 --> 00:26:44,120
♪Lost in sorrow without you♪

930
00:26:44,120 --> 00:26:49,870
♪So weak and helpless♪

931
00:26:49,870 --> 00:26:51,720
(This door only opens in darkness)

932
00:26:51,720 --> 00:26:54,800
This door only opens in darkness.

933
00:26:57,360 --> 00:26:58,080
Turn off the lights.

934
00:26:58,080 --> 00:27:00,440
Wen has the Lights Out Card.

935
00:27:00,440 --> 00:27:00,920
Wen.

936
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:03,160
(My legs are weak)
Can we leave them on?

937
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:04,160
Leave them on.

938
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:05,120
It's okay.

939
00:27:05,120 --> 00:27:06,480
For once on this show,

940
00:27:06,480 --> 00:27:08,080
we know the lights will go off.

941
00:27:08,080 --> 00:27:09,280
So we can prepare.

942
00:27:09,900 --> 00:27:10,800
(Just my luck)

943
00:27:10,800 --> 00:27:11,360
I guess

944
00:27:11,360 --> 00:27:13,240
after the lights go off,

945
00:27:13,240 --> 00:27:14,840
something unknown awaits inside.

946
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:16,120
(Preparing them mentally)
Maybe

947
00:27:16,120 --> 00:27:17,920
the bandaged-face guy will show up.

948
00:27:17,920 --> 00:27:18,400
Exactly.

949
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:19,840
I have a Soothing Card.

950
00:27:19,840 --> 00:27:21,240
I can soothe him.

951
00:27:21,240 --> 00:27:21,840
Use it.

952
00:27:21,840 --> 00:27:22,840
I have a Copy Card.

953
00:27:22,840 --> 00:27:23,720
Use it too.

954
00:27:23,720 --> 00:27:24,960
(Not going farther?)
Double soothing.

955
00:27:24,960 --> 00:27:25,680
We can soothe two.

956
00:27:26,840 --> 00:27:27,520
First, we should

957
00:27:27,520 --> 00:27:28,800
stay really close together.

958
00:27:28,800 --> 00:27:30,560
That way, no one can...

959
00:27:30,560 --> 00:27:31,600
What about my back?

960
00:27:31,620 --> 00:27:32,480
(No one's got his back)

961
00:27:32,480 --> 00:27:33,600
Face your back inside.

962
00:27:36,480 --> 00:27:37,840
That's even scarier.

963
00:27:38,160 --> 00:27:38,680
How about this?

964
00:27:38,680 --> 00:27:38,920
Come here.

965
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:40,280
Let's keep our backs to the inside.

966
00:27:40,280 --> 00:27:40,880
Well then...

967
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:42,480
Facing front is scary too.

968
00:27:43,080 --> 00:27:44,520
(Jump scare risk)
Facing front is scary too.

969
00:27:44,840 --> 00:27:45,120
Wait.

970
00:27:45,120 --> 00:27:46,400
Listen to me.

971
00:27:46,720 --> 00:27:48,120
You turn off the lights.

972
00:27:48,120 --> 00:27:49,280
I'll open the door.

973
00:27:49,280 --> 00:27:51,520
(Taking the lead)
Then I'll check

974
00:27:51,520 --> 00:27:52,640
if it's safe.

975
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:53,720
If it's safe,

976
00:27:53,720 --> 00:27:54,480
I'll call you over.

977
00:27:54,480 --> 00:27:54,920
Okay?

978
00:27:54,920 --> 00:27:56,400
(He really...)
You've grown up.

979
00:27:56,620 --> 00:27:57,700
(Praised by Chengxin)

980
00:27:57,720 --> 00:27:59,560
I'll clear the way for you.

981
00:27:59,560 --> 00:28:00,000
Okay?

982
00:28:00,240 --> 00:28:02,160
Since when did you become our shield?

983
00:28:02,160 --> 00:28:03,120
Can this light up?

984
00:28:03,640 --> 00:28:04,880
Bai isn't here anymore.

985
00:28:04,880 --> 00:28:06,000
I'm scared too, actually.

986
00:28:06,000 --> 00:28:06,860
(I grew up and became him)

987
00:28:08,600 --> 00:28:09,720
Okay, lights off.

988
00:28:09,820 --> 00:28:12,060
(Protection mode: on)

989
00:28:12,560 --> 00:28:13,120
Wait.

990
00:28:13,120 --> 00:28:14,080
You can turn them off, right?

991
00:28:14,080 --> 00:28:14,560
Yes.

992
00:28:14,620 --> 00:28:15,940
(Skill Card)

993
00:28:15,940 --> 00:28:17,680
(Lights Out Card:
Turns off the lights once)

994
00:28:17,680 --> 00:28:19,480
Night falls. Close your eyes.

995
00:28:24,660 --> 00:28:26,260
(Night Vision)

996
00:28:26,960 --> 00:28:27,800
Okay. It's fine.

997
00:28:27,800 --> 00:28:28,720
It's okay.

998
00:28:30,280 --> 00:28:31,000
I'm opening it.

999
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:32,600
Alright.

1000
00:28:33,120 --> 00:28:33,760
Wait.

1001
00:28:33,760 --> 00:28:34,920
Someone hold me from behind.

1002
00:28:36,320 --> 00:28:36,800
Pull it.

1003
00:28:37,360 --> 00:28:38,120
What are you doing?

1004
00:28:38,120 --> 00:28:38,960
(Helping with eyes shut)
I want to pull too.

1005
00:28:38,960 --> 00:28:40,000
Just pull it open.

1006
00:28:40,600 --> 00:28:41,560
Pull.

1007
00:28:42,120 --> 00:28:42,760
Pull.

1008
00:28:42,760 --> 00:28:43,440
Stop pulling.

1009
00:28:43,440 --> 00:28:44,200
(He really pulled)
It's off.

1010
00:28:44,200 --> 00:28:44,520
It's all pulled off.

1011
00:28:44,520 --> 00:28:45,920
We really pulled it all off.

1012
00:28:46,120 --> 00:28:47,320
I'm dying here.

1013
00:28:49,240 --> 00:28:49,520
It's open.

1014
00:28:50,200 --> 00:28:50,720
Okay.

1015
00:28:50,740 --> 00:28:52,020
(Watch the glass. Stay safe.)

1016
00:28:55,620 --> 00:28:56,220
(Night Vision)

1017
00:28:56,280 --> 00:28:57,160
Okay, let's go in.

1018
00:28:57,160 --> 00:28:57,800
Go in.

1019
00:29:00,160 --> 00:29:00,920
There's light.

1020
00:29:01,360 --> 00:29:02,480
(Lit area ahead)
We can see now.

1021
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:04,120
(Night Vision)
Open your eyes, Ding.

1022
00:29:04,120 --> 00:29:05,480
I don't dare.

1023
00:29:05,480 --> 00:29:06,400
(Scaring himself)
♪I don't dare open my eyes♪

1024
00:29:06,400 --> 00:29:08,240
♪I hope this is just in my mind♪

1025
00:29:08,960 --> 00:29:09,440
Let's just

1026
00:29:09,440 --> 00:29:10,720
head toward the light first,

1027
00:29:10,720 --> 00:29:11,200
okay?

1028
00:29:12,280 --> 00:29:13,240
This is a...

1029
00:29:13,560 --> 00:29:14,120
study?

1030
00:29:18,600 --> 00:29:19,200
Archive room.

1031
00:29:19,380 --> 00:29:21,820
(New Area Unlocked: Archive Room)

1032
00:29:22,760 --> 00:29:23,680
Okay.

1033
00:29:23,680 --> 00:29:24,680
I'm really...

1034
00:29:24,680 --> 00:29:25,760
I'm done.

1035
00:29:25,760 --> 00:29:26,560
I need a moment.

1036
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:28,120
Look at this.

1037
00:29:29,960 --> 00:29:30,400
A symbol.

1038
00:29:30,660 --> 00:29:31,600
(Family curse symbol found)

1039
00:29:31,600 --> 00:29:32,160
An X and a circle.

1040
00:29:33,680 --> 00:29:34,760
There's an outfit here.

1041
00:29:35,920 --> 00:29:37,200
This is that Puppet

1042
00:29:37,680 --> 00:29:38,480
from earlier.

1043
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:39,480
The first time

1044
00:29:39,480 --> 00:29:40,360
I saw him in the dark,

1045
00:29:40,360 --> 00:29:42,200
he looked exactly like this.

1046
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:45,860
(Props were specially made.
Filmed safely.)

1047
00:29:45,860 --> 00:29:47,900
(Why is the puppet outfit
in the archive room?)

1048
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:50,200
This is the Puppet-Man's hideout.

1049
00:29:50,260 --> 00:29:52,300
(The archive room was his hideout)

1050
00:29:52,320 --> 00:29:53,400
Why call him "Puppet-Man"?

1051
00:29:54,520 --> 00:29:55,360
Why give him

1052
00:29:55,360 --> 00:29:56,160
such a cool name?

1053
00:29:56,620 --> 00:29:57,720
(Sounds heroic now)

1054
00:29:57,720 --> 00:29:58,640
He's a curse.

1055
00:30:00,240 --> 00:30:00,760
Let's just...

1056
00:30:01,560 --> 00:30:02,120
look around.

1057
00:30:05,280 --> 00:30:06,160
I can't do this.

1058
00:30:07,040 --> 00:30:07,880
Check the drawers.

1059
00:30:11,660 --> 00:30:13,020
(File box)

1060
00:30:15,320 --> 00:30:16,240
There's something here.

1061
00:30:17,160 --> 00:30:17,560
What?

1062
00:30:19,060 --> 00:30:21,140
(Torn paper pieces)

1063
00:30:21,160 --> 00:30:21,600
An San.

1064
00:30:21,600 --> 00:30:22,240
An San?

1065
00:30:24,040 --> 00:30:24,760
There are two.

1066
00:30:25,760 --> 00:30:26,840
These are our late

1067
00:30:26,840 --> 00:30:28,800
aunt and uncle.

1068
00:30:30,960 --> 00:30:32,400
The cursed family victims.

1069
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:33,540
(An San and An Si, killed by the curse)

1070
00:30:33,920 --> 00:30:35,520
But this happened

1071
00:30:35,520 --> 00:30:36,840
twenty years ago.

1072
00:30:36,840 --> 00:30:38,800
Why is it happening again?

1073
00:30:39,600 --> 00:30:42,120
An San died

1074
00:30:42,120 --> 00:30:44,520
on March 25, 1996.

1075
00:30:45,000 --> 00:30:45,480
An San.

1076
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:47,400
Family curse. An Si.

1077
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:48,360
Her death

1078
00:30:48,360 --> 00:30:51,640
was on March 25, 1978.

1079
00:30:51,820 --> 00:30:53,120
(First Curse. Second Curse.)

1080
00:30:53,120 --> 00:30:54,000
Who's this?

1081
00:30:54,400 --> 00:30:55,280
There's someone there. It's creepy.

1082
00:30:55,280 --> 00:30:55,800
There's a person.

1083
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:56,320
Look at the photo.

1084
00:30:57,180 --> 00:30:58,940
(Who is the woman behind An Si?)

1085
00:30:58,960 --> 00:31:00,240
What a terrifying photo.

1086
00:31:00,660 --> 00:31:01,820
(Jumpscared by a paper cutout)

1087
00:31:02,360 --> 00:31:02,880
What happened?

1088
00:31:02,880 --> 00:31:03,360
Nothing.

1089
00:31:03,360 --> 00:31:03,760
What happened?

1090
00:31:03,760 --> 00:31:04,840
Nothing. Don't be scared.

1091
00:31:04,840 --> 00:31:06,520
It's a woman with no clear face.

1092
00:31:07,360 --> 00:31:08,480
An Si...

1093
00:31:08,480 --> 00:31:09,880
An Si is my fourth brother.

1094
00:31:10,320 --> 00:31:10,800
Your fourth brother?

1095
00:31:10,800 --> 00:31:11,560
(An Si is An Ke's full brother)
He's my brother.

1096
00:31:11,560 --> 00:31:12,520
He's my fourth brother.

1097
00:31:12,520 --> 00:31:13,080
She's my third sister.

1098
00:31:13,520 --> 00:31:15,480
Then this must be An Si's mother.

1099
00:31:15,620 --> 00:31:17,700
(An Songqiu and his first wife:
An Yi, An Er, An San)

1100
00:31:17,700 --> 00:31:20,060
(An Songqiu and his second wife:
An Si, An Ke)

1101
00:31:20,060 --> 00:31:21,980
(Family curse victims: An San and An Si)

1102
00:31:23,600 --> 00:31:24,960
After An Si died,

1103
00:31:24,960 --> 00:31:26,400
his mother vanished.

1104
00:31:26,880 --> 00:31:28,920
She's An Songqiu's second wife.

1105
00:31:28,980 --> 00:31:29,680
(An Songqiu and his first wife:
An Yi, An Er, An San)

1106
00:31:29,680 --> 00:31:30,800
(An Songqiu and second wife: An Si, An Ke)
This is your mom?

1107
00:31:30,800 --> 00:31:31,120
Not sure.

1108
00:31:31,120 --> 00:31:32,360
(An Ke's mom vanished when he was six)
You can't see her face.

1109
00:31:32,360 --> 00:31:33,280
How would you know?

1110
00:31:33,280 --> 00:31:34,840
It might not be his mom.

1111
00:31:35,380 --> 00:31:38,060
(Who is the mystery woman?)

1112
00:31:39,280 --> 00:31:41,600
Then why is this here?

1113
00:31:42,240 --> 00:31:43,440
Look at this.

1114
00:31:43,500 --> 00:31:44,580
(There's a mark on the back)

1115
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:46,160
The backs fit together.

1116
00:31:46,160 --> 00:31:47,000
It's an X and a circle.

1117
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:52,000
The curse again.

1118
00:31:54,680 --> 00:31:56,640
There's another X-circle here.

1119
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:00,520
Let's piece them together.

1120
00:32:00,520 --> 00:32:01,320
Okay, come on.

1121
00:32:01,320 --> 00:32:01,800
Hurry.

1122
00:32:01,800 --> 00:32:02,320
Once we do,

1123
00:32:02,320 --> 00:32:03,560
will it trigger something?

1124
00:32:03,560 --> 00:32:03,840
Maybe.

1125
00:32:03,840 --> 00:32:04,120
Yeah.

1126
00:32:04,120 --> 00:32:04,600
It's possible.

1127
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:05,920
Brace yourselves.

1128
00:32:05,920 --> 00:32:06,560
I'm ready.

1129
00:32:08,320 --> 00:32:09,280
Will it come alive?

1130
00:32:09,280 --> 00:32:10,680
(Nervous)
It won't.

1131
00:32:10,680 --> 00:32:11,360
You never know.

1132
00:32:11,360 --> 00:32:12,280
Wait. I'll poke it.

1133
00:32:12,280 --> 00:32:12,760
Poke it.

1134
00:32:13,560 --> 00:32:14,280
It's fake.

1135
00:32:14,280 --> 00:32:15,480
I already checked it.

1136
00:32:16,880 --> 00:32:17,960
It's fine. I've got my Golden Staff.

1137
00:32:21,360 --> 00:32:22,760
Why am I such a coward?

1138
00:32:22,760 --> 00:32:23,920
I'm so done with myself.

1139
00:32:23,920 --> 00:32:25,040
(So disappointed in himself)

1140
00:32:25,040 --> 00:32:26,360
Can I act like a man?

1141
00:32:26,360 --> 00:32:27,160
(Roasting himself hard)

1142
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:28,720
It's fine. Fear is physical.

1143
00:32:28,720 --> 00:32:29,440
It has nothing

1144
00:32:29,440 --> 00:32:30,200
to do with

1145
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:31,000
being a man.

1146
00:32:31,020 --> 00:32:31,840
(Men can be scared too)

1147
00:32:31,840 --> 00:32:32,640
Last piece, guys.

1148
00:32:39,720 --> 00:32:40,160
Here we go.

1149
