Don't do this.

1150
00:32:47,080 --> 00:32:47,600
Red light.

1151
00:32:48,440 --> 00:32:49,000
Wait.

1152
00:32:49,000 --> 00:32:50,640
What did they say the laser was?

1153
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:51,520
This one's red.

1154
00:32:51,520 --> 00:32:52,720
Last time, it was green.

1155
00:32:52,980 --> 00:32:55,460
(File bag)

1156
00:32:55,760 --> 00:32:56,920
Ding, are you okay?

1157
00:32:56,920 --> 00:32:57,520
No.

1158
00:32:57,520 --> 00:32:58,640
Want to hold the staff?

1159
00:32:58,640 --> 00:32:59,600
(Helping each other)
You can take it.

1160
00:32:59,600 --> 00:33:00,280
Okay.

1161
00:33:07,960 --> 00:33:08,520
The light changed.

1162
00:33:08,520 --> 00:33:10,420
