1163
00:33:11,000 --> 00:33:11,560
It changed.

1164
00:33:18,080 --> 00:33:18,880
Kind of cool.

1165
00:33:22,040 --> 00:33:23,080
White light.

1166
00:33:23,080 --> 00:33:24,120
What color was it before?

1167
00:33:25,080 --> 00:33:26,040
No one's coming, right?

1168
00:33:26,040 --> 00:33:26,520
No way.

1169
00:33:28,120 --> 00:33:28,600
It's over.

1170
00:33:32,440 --> 00:33:33,400
What does that mean?

1171
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:35,380
(What just happened?)

1172
00:33:35,880 --> 00:33:36,560
What's going on?

1173
00:33:43,560 --> 00:33:44,320
Firecrackers.

1174
00:33:45,740 --> 00:33:47,420
(Why are there firecrackers?)

1175
00:33:47,440 --> 00:33:48,280
Firecrackers. Come on.

1176
00:33:48,880 --> 00:33:49,480
Hurry, go.

1177
00:33:49,580 --> 00:33:50,720
(Refuses to be last)

1178
00:33:50,720 --> 00:33:52,160
Hurry.

1179
00:33:52,760 --> 00:33:53,320
Firecrackers.

1180
00:33:55,720 --> 00:33:57,600
My steps just sped up.

1181
00:33:57,600 --> 00:33:59,040
I feel light on my feet now.

1182
00:34:00,640 --> 00:34:01,520
Who are you?

1183
00:34:02,000 --> 00:34:02,480
Hello.

1184
00:34:02,480 --> 00:34:03,840
I'm the security guard here.

1185
00:34:04,140 --> 00:34:04,800
(A stranger appears)

1186
00:34:04,800 --> 00:34:06,160
I'll take you over there.

1187
00:34:06,960 --> 00:34:07,640
Where?

1188
00:34:07,640 --> 00:34:08,480
It's raining, everyone.

1189
00:34:08,480 --> 00:34:09,190
I'll take you there.

1190
00:34:09,190 --> 00:34:10,040
Grab an umbrella.

1191
00:34:12,080 --> 00:34:13,360
Why is it dark now?

1192
00:34:13,800 --> 00:34:15,360
Yeah. What happened?

1193
00:34:15,840 --> 00:34:16,880
Let's go first.

1194
00:34:16,880 --> 00:34:18,880
An Glass Factory.

1195
00:34:18,880 --> 00:34:20,860
(An Glass Factory)

1196
00:34:20,860 --> 00:34:22,420
(An Residence Entrance)

1197
00:34:23,480 --> 00:34:24,760
What are we doing here?

1198
00:34:38,190 --> 00:34:39,560
There's a show here?

1199
00:34:44,080 --> 00:34:45,190
Who's getting married?

1200
00:34:45,190 --> 00:34:46,260
(They've arrived at a wedding)

1201
00:34:48,020 --> 00:34:49,460
(What is going on?)

1202
00:34:50,900 --> 00:34:52,380
(We're here anyway. Might as well party)

1203
00:34:57,520 --> 00:34:58,480
Hurry, get in there.

1204
00:35:10,620 --> 00:35:12,860
(Dance moves synced)

1205
00:35:13,100 --> 00:35:14,580
(Zero delay)

1206
00:35:19,900 --> 00:35:22,340
(Nunchuck-style dancing)

1207
00:35:22,380 --> 00:35:24,100
(Wiggle)

1208
00:35:24,180 --> 00:35:26,180
(Looking around)

1209
00:35:28,260 --> 00:35:30,620
(Clearly never took dance lessons)

1210
00:35:30,700 --> 00:35:33,020
("Ning's Fancy Footwork")

1211
00:35:33,020 --> 00:35:34,620
(With "Ning Family Fist")

1212
00:35:39,220 --> 00:35:42,020
(Right in his element)

1213
00:35:48,980 --> 00:35:51,260
(Here comes the ace)

1214
00:35:52,740 --> 00:35:54,140
(Signature move)

1215
00:35:55,280 --> 00:35:57,000
Floor move. Leg sweep.

1216
00:35:57,560 --> 00:35:59,280
Nice!

1217
00:35:59,920 --> 00:36:00,840
Good!

1218
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:01,560
Dance!

1219
00:36:04,380 --> 00:36:05,340
(A little tribute)

1220
00:36:12,600 --> 00:36:13,760
He even has an ending pose.

1221
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:14,240
Ending!

1222
00:36:16,780 --> 00:36:18,660
(Facial control on point)

1223
00:36:19,000 --> 00:36:21,440
(Extra scenes 12 PM every Sat)
Okay, music off!

1224
00:36:21,440 --> 00:36:21,680
Come on.

1225
00:36:21,680 --> 00:36:23,560
(Host)
Dancers, please head off and rest!

1226
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:24,800
Sir, you look like

1227
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:27,040
you're good with a bow.

1228
00:36:27,680 --> 00:36:29,160
Seen my other side gigs, huh?

1229
00:36:30,760 --> 00:36:31,000
Okay.

1230
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:31,760
Dear guests,

1231
00:36:31,760 --> 00:36:32,920
