1356
00:40:23,640 --> 00:40:25,920
We need one more guy

1357
00:40:25,920 --> 00:40:27,760
to be a bridesmaid.

1358
00:40:29,880 --> 00:40:31,680
A guy as a bridesmaid?

1359
00:40:31,920 --> 00:40:32,600
Why?

1360
00:40:32,600 --> 00:40:33,120
Here's the thing.

1361
00:40:33,120 --> 00:40:33,880
Someone from their family

1362
00:40:33,880 --> 00:40:35,320
is joining as a groomsman.

1363
00:40:35,320 --> 00:40:36,760
So, now we need three bridesmaids.

1364
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:37,560
(Urgently hiring bridesmaid. Any gender)
Still one short.

1365
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:38,760
So one of us

1366
00:40:38,760 --> 00:40:39,920
needs to be a bridesmaid.

1367
00:40:40,360 --> 00:40:41,360
Rock paper scissors. Loser goes.

1368
00:40:42,200 --> 00:40:42,720
Let's go.

1369
00:40:42,720 --> 00:40:44,120
(Competing for the spot)
Rock paper scissors!

1370
00:40:44,180 --> 00:40:45,100
(Scissors vs. fist)

1371
00:40:45,620 --> 00:40:46,720
(The groom watches with amusement)

1372
00:40:46,720 --> 00:40:47,320
You two.

1373
00:40:47,320 --> 00:40:47,860
(Bridesmaid playoff)

1374
00:40:48,880 --> 00:40:49,800
No way.

1375
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:50,560
Hold on.

1376
00:40:50,560 --> 00:40:50,960
Okay.

1377
00:40:51,520 --> 00:40:52,640
I'm not getting any younger.

1378
00:40:52,640 --> 00:40:53,040
Come on.

1379
00:40:53,040 --> 00:40:53,360
It's fine, Ning.

1380
00:40:53,360 --> 00:40:53,640
Come on.

1381
00:40:53,640 --> 00:40:55,040
Rock paper scissors!

1382
00:40:55,040 --> 00:40:55,760
It's fine, I can go.

1383
00:40:55,760 --> 00:40:56,580
(So gracious)
Really, it's fine.

1384
00:40:56,720 --> 00:40:57,240
No!

1385
00:40:57,240 --> 00:40:57,640
Hold on!

1386
00:41:00,600 --> 00:41:01,600
I want to go.

1387
00:41:02,040 --> 00:41:02,960
Okay.

1388
00:41:02,960 --> 00:41:03,480
Perfect.

1389
00:41:03,480 --> 00:41:04,440
A deal's a deal.

1390
00:41:04,440 --> 00:41:05,840
Destiny!

1391
00:41:06,920 --> 00:41:08,560
So the groom is...

1392
00:41:08,560 --> 00:41:09,120
Me.

1393
00:41:09,120 --> 00:41:09,680
You it is.

1394
00:41:10,120 --> 00:41:11,520
And the bridesmaid is you.

1395
00:41:11,520 --> 00:41:11,840
Yep.

1396
00:41:11,840 --> 00:41:12,360
Everyone else

1397
00:41:12,360 --> 00:41:13,880
just play your actual gender.

1398
00:41:13,880 --> 00:41:14,280
Got it.

1399
00:41:14,280 --> 00:41:15,040
Yes.

1400
00:41:15,960 --> 00:41:16,760
Come on, everyone check

1401
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:18,120
