(Bodyguard, He Jiahuan)
I am a bodyguard.

2822
01:25:24,800 --> 01:25:27,040
Your rank is one level above mine.

2823
01:25:27,040 --> 01:25:28,560
I am a bodyguard, not a security guard.

2824
01:25:29,240 --> 01:25:29,640
A bodyguard.

2825
01:25:29,640 --> 01:25:30,800
That identity sounds impressive.

2826
01:25:30,800 --> 01:25:32,160
I am a personal bodyguard.

2827
01:25:32,160 --> 01:25:33,300
(Personal bodyguard)

2828
01:25:35,640 --> 01:25:36,000
No.

2829
01:25:36,000 --> 01:25:37,960
The restriction on entering
the wedding chamber

2830
01:25:37,960 --> 01:25:39,280
was from the 1996 timeline, correct?

2831
01:25:39,280 --> 01:25:40,040
The events of 1996.

2832
01:25:41,040 --> 01:25:42,120
(No entry to the wedding chamber)
It's all here, right?

2833
01:25:42,120 --> 01:25:43,280
Which side do we change clothes on?

2834
01:25:43,280 --> 01:25:43,840
The left side.

2835
01:25:44,440 --> 01:25:45,400
Why are there uniforms here

2836
01:25:45,400 --> 01:25:46,120
when we returned?

2837
01:25:46,120 --> 01:25:48,040
How did I suddenly
become a security guard?

2838
01:25:48,040 --> 01:25:49,680
Why are there uniforms here?

2839
01:25:50,160 --> 01:25:51,560
Wait a moment. Our identities...

2840
01:25:53,100 --> 01:25:58,220
(If this is neither 2016 nor 1996,
then what year is it?)

2841
01:25:58,300 --> 01:26:02,140
(What year are we actually in?)

2842
01:26:02,160 --> 01:26:03,000
(Next Episode Preview)
I have An Yi's

2843
01:26:03,000 --> 01:26:04,440
medical examination report.

2844
01:26:05,360 --> 01:26:06,080
He is not dead.

2845
01:26:06,080 --> 01:26:06,960
He is still alive.

2846
01:26:06,960 --> 01:26:08,720
Something is becoming very wrong.

2847
01:26:08,720 --> 01:26:10,120
Then whose corpse was it?

2848
01:26:10,120 --> 01:26:11,880
One of the four of us.

2849
01:26:12,560 --> 01:26:13,360
A paradox.

2850
01:26:13,520 --> 01:26:14,680
If you burn someone,

2851
01:26:14,680 --> 01:26:15,760
then it becomes yours.

2852
01:26:15,760 --> 01:26:16,920
I am ready to identify the killer.

2853
01:26:16,980 --> 01:26:18,240
(In the name of "love",
the curse repeats itself)

2854
01:26:18,240 --> 01:26:20,480
This is a curse that has haunted
the An family.

2855
01:26:20,560 --> 01:26:21,480
The child is gone.

2856
01:26:21,480 --> 01:26:23,360
I don't want this cycle
to continue any longer.

2857
01:26:23,360 --> 01:26:24,960
Say goodbye to domestic violence.

2858
01:26:24,960 --> 01:26:26,280
We must save the children.

2859
01:26:26,280 --> 01:26:27,840
Although this method
of education is painful,

2860
01:26:27,840 --> 01:26:29,880
perhaps there is some
justification behind it.

2861
01:26:29,880 --> 01:26:30,640
Emotional abuse.

2862
01:26:30,640 --> 01:26:31,680
Excessive psychological control.

2863
01:26:31,680 --> 01:26:33,120
Talk back again
and I'll beat you to death.

2864
01:26:33,120 --> 01:26:34,840
They all think they're
doing the right thing.

2865
01:26:34,840 --> 01:26:36,440
Look how well I have raised my child.

2866
01:26:36,440 --> 01:26:37,880
And yet you resorted to violence.

2867
01:26:37,880 --> 01:26:39,480
You are a monster.

2868
01:26:39,480 --> 01:26:39,960
Wait.

2869
01:26:40,880 --> 01:26:41,240
It's alive.

2870
01:26:42,400 --> 01:26:43,360
It is actually alive.

2871
01:26:45,120 --> 01:26:45,840
That is terrifying.

2872
01:26:46,440 --> 01:26:47,840
I love everyone.

2873
01:26:47,840 --> 01:26:49,480
My methods may simply be different.

2874
01:26:49,480 --> 01:26:51,040
I, too, am someone

2875
01:26:51,040 --> 01:26:52,800
who insists on achieving my goals.

2876
01:26:52,800 --> 01:26:53,880
You sinner.

2877
01:26:53,880 --> 01:26:55,400
You are a selfish person.

2878
01:26:55,400 --> 01:26:58,000
Psychologically, you are deeply
disturbed in every respect.

2879
01:26:58,280 --> 01:26:59,120
It was all of us together

2880
01:26:59,120 --> 01:27:00,640
who brought about this tragedy.

2881
01:27:49,800 --> 01:27:53,800
♪Come now, players all,
let the game of reason start♪

2882
01:27:53,800 --> 01:27:58,240
♪Unlock each hidden trial,
let courage spark the dark♪

2883
01:28:00,260 --> 01:28:04,420
♪Night falls slow, shadows grow,
the sleuth is lost inside the maze♪

2884
01:28:04,420 --> 01:28:08,640
♪Figures pass, lanterns sparse,
dark currents drift without a trace♪

2885
01:28:08,640 --> 01:28:12,410
♪Wind picks up, footsteps rush,
cold laughter swallowed by the dark♪

2886
01:28:12,410 --> 01:28:16,520
♪Truth concealed, the night
stands still, and nothing leaves a mark♪

2887
01:28:16,700 --> 01:28:20,820
♪An unsigned letter, coded words,
the solvers gather one by one♪

2888
01:28:20,820 --> 01:28:24,930
♪A broken game, illusion reigns,
who's hiding what they've done?♪

2889
01:28:24,930 --> 01:28:28,570
♪Hushed voices, nerves on edge,
wrapped in smoke and mirrors still♪

2890
01:28:28,570 --> 01:28:30,700
♪The next second, deeper riddles,
or the answer to the kill♪

2891
01:28:30,700 --> 01:28:34,650
♪Every piece of truth
has finally come to light♪

2892
01:28:34,890 --> 01:28:38,810
♪Unlock the mystery, turn the question,
let's begin tonight♪

2893
01:28:39,020 --> 01:28:43,170
♪Side by side, no holding back,
follow every clue to find the truth♪

2894
01:28:43,170 --> 01:28:46,730
♪The story blurs like flowers in fog,
let's begin tonight♪

2895
01:28:46,990 --> 01:28:51,640
♪Search for the vanished cipher,
trace the proof, and face the sleuth♪
